The solution of the test set issued on the course FlatSchool.com

«адание є1
--------------
  1
  11
  21
  1211
  111221
  ѕродолжите строки
  
    –ешение: 
    -----------------------------------------
      text = "1" # начальный номер
      for k in 1..15 # количество строк 15
        num = out = ""
        kol = 0
        for i in 0..text.length-1
          num = text[i] if i == 0
          sym = text[i]
          if num != sym
            out << kol.to_s << num.to_s
            num = sym
            kol = 0
          end
          kol+=1
        end
        puts text
        text = out << kol.to_s << num.to_s
      end


